<number box="[716,774,705,729]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30" value="1922.0">1922</number>
a)
</bibRefCitation>
from 
<collectingCountry box="[862,1069,705,729]" name="Equatorial Guinea" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">Equatorial Guinea</collectingCountry>
. The 
<typeStatus box="[1130,1228,705,729]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">holotype</typeStatus>
has not been studied and it has been identified from the original description and identified material in 
<collectionCode box="[1098,1184,741,765]" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/z14b-bb31" name="Musée Royal de l’Afrique Centrale" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">MRAC</collectionCode>
.
</paragraph>
