<subSubSection lastPageId="30" lastPageNumber="31" pageId="29" pageNumber="30" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="29.[151,1436,705,945]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,321,777,802]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Female. Vestiture on head black, mesosoma mostly black, posterolateral and posterior regions white, legs black, T 
<number box="[373,383,813,837]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30" value="1.0">1</number>
white, T 
<number box="[483,496,813,837]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30" value="2.0">2</number>
–T 
<number box="[528,542,813,837]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30" value="4.0">4</number>
black, T 
<number box="[640,652,813,837]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30" value="5.0">5</number>
–T 
<number box="[685,698,813,837]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30" value="6.0">6</number>
orange, scopa orange (
<figureCitation box="[955,1081,813,837]" captionStart="FIGURE 20 a – b" captionStartId="29.[151,250,1999,2022]" captionTargetBox="[151,1420,998,1970]" captionTargetId="figure@29.[151,1436,998,1976]" captionTargetPageId="29" captionText="FIGURE 20 a – b. Megachile trichroma, female. a. Face. b. Habitus" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/246145/files/figure.png" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">
Fig. 
<number box="[1007,1037,813,837]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30" value="20.0">20</number>
a–b
</figureCitation>
). Lengths: face 
<quantity box="[1256,1344,813,837]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.4" pageId="29" pageNumber="30" unit="mm" value="4.4">4.4 mm</quantity>
; scutum 
<quantity box="[151,242,849,873]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.5" pageId="29" pageNumber="30" unit="mm" value="3.5">3.5 mm</quantity>
; forewing 12.0 mm; body 17.0 mm. Structure. Clypeus 
<number box="[882,917,849,873]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30" value="2.5">2.5</number>
times as wide as long, convex and punctuate above, flat and punctuate below, not tuberculate ventrolaterally, ventral edge slightly concave mediolaterally, pointed medially (
<figureCitation box="[355,439,921,945]" captionStart="FIGURE 20 a – b" captionStartId="29.[151,250,1999,2022]" captionTargetBox="[151,1420,998,1970]" captionTargetId="figure@29.[151,1436,998,1976]" captionTargetPageId="29" captionText="FIGURE 20 a – b. Megachile trichroma, female. a. Face. b. Habitus" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/246145/files/figure.png" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">
Fig. 
<number box="[407,439,921,945]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30" value="20.0">20</number>
</figureCitation>
c); clypeocellus: clypeus 
<number box="[719,730,921,945]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30" value="1.0">1</number>
: 
<number box="[734,778,921,945]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30" value="0.5">0.5</number>
; scopal hairs blunt and thickened distally.
</paragraph>
<caption box="[151,830,1999,2022]" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/246145/files/figure.png" pageId="29" pageNumber="30" targetBox="[151,1420,998,1970]" targetPageId="29">
